Tanyakan dia.

00:16:08.800 --> 00:16:09.960
Apakah Anda menemukan Parineet?

00:16:11.200 --> 00:16:13.160
Bibi, Parineet
tidak ada di kuil.

00:16:13.200 --> 00:16:14.240
Dia

00:16:14.800 --> 00:16:15.960
menuju ke arah gunung.

00:16:17.360 --> 00:16:18.520
Gunung!

00:16:18.800 --> 00:16:20.520
Apakah dia bunuh diri?

00:16:20.600 --> 00:16:21.720
Hei, tidak..
